Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 06 of Thoracic CT
And I select 'Finding' radio button
And I select 'Characterization' tab

When I select 'Increased parenchymal density' from Finding dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding button' is enabled
And 'Consolidation' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ground-Glass Opacity, GGO' checkbox is enabled
And 'Pleural thickening' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Consolidation' checkbox
Then the multiple selection 'Distribution' localizer is enabled
And 'Positive bronchopneumogram' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Consolidation' checkbox
Then the multiple selection 'Distribution' localizer is enabled
And 'Quantity' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Ratio reticular changes/ground glass opacities' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'Dark bronchus sign' checkbox is enabled
